<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 34 (August 19th, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The flat basic attack damage bonus granted by the Stackable Passive: Precision has been reduced to 20, down from 25.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 33 (July 29th, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The flat basic attack damage increase from the Unique Passive: Exploit Weakness has been increased to 25, up from 10.</li><li>Fixed a bug where the basic attack damage increase from this ability was unintentionally applying to abilities in addition to basic attacks.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 31 (June 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The Haste granted by this item has been increased to 35, up from 30.</li><li>The damage amplification granted by the Exploit Weakness Unique Passive has been increased to 5% per stack, up from 4%.</li><li>The price of this item has been increased to 3000, up from 2670.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 28.1 (April 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The damage amplification of the Exploit Weakness Unique Passive has been increased to 4% bonus damage per stack, up from 3%.</li><li>The price of this item has been increased to 2670, up from 2490.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Added to the game.</li></ul>